<script>
  'use strict';

  export let user = { loggedIn: false };

  function toggle () {
    user.loggedIn = !user.loggedIn;
  }
</script>


{#if user.loggedIn}
  <button on:click={toggle}>
    Log out
  </button>
{:else}
  <button on:click={toggle}>
    Log in
  </button>
{/if}
